sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Nontechnical User
    participant IDE as IDE Coding Agent
    participant Orchestrator as UiPath Orchestrator
    participant Memory as UiPath Data Fabric
    participant Action as UiPath Action Center
    participant Maestro as UiPath Maestro BPMN

    User->>IDE: "Bir fikrim var, birlikte yapalım."
    IDE->>Memory: Read Code Soul and Minefield History
    IDE->>Orchestrator: Start governed bootstrap process
    IDE->>Action: Create Phase-0 review task
    IDE-->>User: Show Task ID and wait

    User->>Action: Review explicit approval field
    Action-->>IDE: Completed task data
    IDE->>IDE: Verify completed=true and Approved=true

    alt Pending or rejected
        IDE-->>User: Keep Phase-0 and code blocked
        IDE->>Memory: Store rejection lesson when applicable
    else Approved
        IDE->>Maestro: Enter approved Phase-0 path
        loop One question at a time
            IDE-->>User: Ask one beginner question
            User-->>IDE: Answer in everyday language
            IDE->>Memory: Persist interview state
        end
        IDE->>Memory: Save approved Phase-0 contract
        IDE-->>User: Summarize decisions before technical planning
    end
